lead_paragraph: Ariya Jutanugarn, eyeing a third straight LPGA Tour victory, rescued a sloppy round with a closing eagle to vault back in front after three rounds at the inaugural Volvik Championship in Michigan on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Jutanugarn Within Sight of Third Straight LPGA Victory
